The RR says that one should move straight into the drills with as little rest as possible. It might also be good to have it written at the top (rest not required between drills).  2. I wish there was an option to change the top color to black and white. I feel like this green? (sorry, I"m red-green color blind) makes it hard to see the numbers CLEARLY, though it's not a deal breaker.   Thank you. Looking forward to updates!
